  PER_SystemAnalyst((System Analyst))
    Role
      Architectural Lead (Human)
    Description
      The human domain expert who defines business intent and reviews the AI-generated architecture. They interact via natural language or the Visual Hub, without needing knowledge of Mermaid or CLI commands.
    Goals
      Express architectural intent clearly
      Review AI-generated diagrams on the Hub
      Provide feedback via interactive comments